posts.post_title: WTB: T206 Cubs, Brown, Tinker, Evers, Chance
posts.post_content:
Hi all.  I’m mostly a postwar guy but am putting together a collection of Cubs greats over the years.  I don’t know much about t206 cards but am searching for examples of Brown, Tinker, Evers, and Chance in PSA/SGC 2.5-4.  I’m looking for a clean image of the front and I don’t care too much about the back type.  Let me know what you have.  Thanks!


Sent from my iPhone using Tapatalk
Good luck.   Did a run on that once.   Tough and expensive.   Very competitive as well to acquire.
